sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User/UI
  participant C as UI API Adapter
  participant H as DataCloudHttpServer
  participant E as EntityCrudHandler
  participant R as Repository/Store
  participant DB as Entity Tables
  U->>C: create/update/list entity or collection
  C->>H: HTTP /api/v1/entities/*
  H->>H: CORS/rate limit/size/optional security
  H->>E: dispatch request
  E->>R: validate and persist/query
  R->>DB: read/write rows
  DB-->>R: result
  R-->>E: entity/result set
  E-->>H: JSON payload
  H-->>C: HTTP response
  C-->>U: render state

